      <div class="glvx-review-body">Bought this as a gift for my mom and she absolutely loves it. Uses it every single day now. The design is so elegant and modern. Already recommended it to 3 of my friends. Amazing product — worth every penny!</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Review 6 -->
    <div class="glvx-review-card">
      <span class="glvx-helpful-tag">✓ Verified Purchase</span>
      <div class="glvx-review-top">
        <div class="glvx-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="glvx-reviewer-info">
          <div class="glvx-reviewer-name">Michael B.</div>
          <div class="glvx-reviewer-meta">
