            <span class="glvx-verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="glvx-review-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <div class="glvx-review-date">April 20, 2026</div>
      <div class="glvx-review-title">Game changer for long work days</div>
      <div class="glvx-review-body">I work 10+ hours a day at a computer and this has become part of my daily routine. Easy to use, comfortable to wear, and the heat setting is a nice bonus. Packaging was premium too. 5 stars without hesitation!</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Review 7 -->
    <div class="glvx-review-card">
      <span class="glvx-helpful-tag">✓ Verified Purchase</span>
      <div class="glvx-review-top">
        <div class="glvx-avatar">L</div>
        <div class="glvx-reviewer-info">
          <div class="glvx-reviewer-name">Lauren H.</div>
          <div class="glvx-reviewer-meta">
            <span class="glvx-reviewer-location">📍 Denver, Colorado</span>
            <span class="glvx-verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="glvx-review-stars">★★★★☆</div>
      <div class="glvx-review-date">May 7, 2026</div>
      <div class="glvx-review-title">Really solid product!</div>
      <div class="glvx-review-body">I was a little skeptical at first but wow — this thing actually works. Takes about 10 minutes to really settle in but once it does it feels amazing. Battery life is great. Would give 5 stars but took a day to figure out the levels. Still highly recommend!</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Load More Button -->
  <div class="glvx-load-more-wrap" id="glvxLoadMoreWrap">
    <button class="glvx-load-more-btn" onclick="glvxLoadMore()">
      See All Reviews →
    </button>
    <p class="glvx-load-more-sub">Showing 4 of 67 reviews</p>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  function glvxLoadMore() {
    document.getElementById('glvxMoreReviews').style.display = 'block';
    document.getElementById('glvxLoadMoreWrap').style.display = 'none';
  }
</script>
